Text: eTicket Receipt PickupThis message is to inform you that your eTicket receipt is available for pickup ECN A the desk of Leticia Flores Pickup time is between am and pm I realize that some of you may not be in the Houston office so if you would like for me to mail the receipt to you please send me the address where you would like it delivered If you feel you have received this message in error feel free to contact me Thank You Corporate Travel Johnny Ross

Airfare Credit SlipsThis message is to inform you that you have Airfare credit slip available to pick up at the desk of Leticia Flores ECNA Pickup times are am to pm Monday Friday I understand that you may not be in Houston or in the Enron Buildings please just email me with an address that we can send your credit slips to If you are in the downtown buildings we will not interoffice mail these Please pick up at your earliest convenience Thank you Corporate Travel Johnny Ross
